Package api

Interface edge_data

All Known Implementing Classes:
EdgeData
public interface edge_data
This interface represents the set of operations applicable on a directional edge(src,dest) in a (directional) weighted graph.
Author:
boaz.benmoshe

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    int getDest()

    java.lang.String getInfo()

    int getTag()
    Temporal data (aka color: e,g, white, gray, black) which can be used be algorithms
